For **Pantheon-Prime**, we can design a lightweight, local-first **Delta-Tracking Video Daemon (d_delta_render)**. Instead of dealing with heavy raw video tensors, it processes video as a one-dimensional temporal sequence of state changes relative to a base "Anchor" image.
